.DT
query_shorts
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_shorts

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_shorts -  This method will return all the shorts for the specified directory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
mapping query_shorts(string dir)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dir%^RESET%^ - the directory to return the shorts for
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the shorts descriptions mapping
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method will return all the shorts for the specified directory.
The mapping returned has keys of the room names and values of the
short description of the room.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
change_shorts()

.EP

